item.title: Awesome Go
item.description:
Awesome Go
Financial support to Awesome Go We have no monthly cost, but we have employees hard working to maintain the Awesome Go, with money raised we can repay the effort of each person involved! A curated list of awesome Go frameworks, libraries and software. Inspired by awesome-python. Contributing Please take a quick gander at the contribution guidelines first. Thanks to all contributors; you rock!
